sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:22:CypherClaw is an autonomous music-making entity that has been running continuously for ~12 days at the time of this PRD, composing through a SuperCollider-driven duet composer with seven voices (pluck, breath, choir, kotekan, pad, bowed, tabla_tin) across scenes whose arc phases cycle Listen / Conversation / Divination / Procession. It currently outputs through one master reverb on a JACK graph and is heard only inside the room where the box lives.
