LEAD agent commit missed test file updates and several internal docstring references. — fixed during verification.\n- [x] Functional mismatch between \"quintet is the orchestra\" comment and `voice_count_ceiling=4`. — fixed by increasing ceiling to 5 for relevant modes.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe initial pass updated the main module docstrings but missed the test suite and some internal dataclass field docstrings. Always check the corresponding test files when changing architectural concepts like ensemble size.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-029@20260425t183959zc-verify.md"}}
