ed files.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [ ] No issues found — severity: none\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\n- The implementation is clean and follows best practices for single-source-of-truth constants.\n- The startup hardening (identity bootstrap) is already correctly integrated into the CLI and Narrative API entry points.\n"}}
