ean, well-documented, and passes all quality gates:\n- `pytest tests/test_asset_bus_paths.py` -> 14 passed.\n- `ruff check` -> clean.\n- `mypy` -> clean.\n\n## Issues Found\n- None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe sanitization layer is robust and ready for integration into `store.py` and the producer runtime.\nCandidate hardening from the log was reviewed; while it mentions SuperCollider synthdefs (not directly related to path sanitization), the general principle of explicit parameter validation was observed in the `sanitize_*` functions.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-001 @20260530t002730z-verify.md"}}
