l 23 tests in `tests/test_usage_journal.py` and the integration test in `tests/test_usage_journal_integration.py` pass.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [x] No issues found.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation of the `source_kind` fallback and the legacy journal-replay tests is solid. The \"Candidate Hardening\" items regarding `bootstrap_identity` were also cross-checked and found to be correctly implemented in all relevant daemon entrypoints.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-019 @20260427t001208zd-verify.md"}}
